Description: Fragment of an amulet of Sekhmet, made of light green faience. Standing figure with sun disc, broken off under breasts and upper arms. A cylindrical hole runs horizontally through the neck. Flat at the rear with a horizontal line like for a back pillar, might have been inscribed.
Findspot: Excavated/Findspot: Amara West (Nubia), D12.1, middle debris
